column2: SELECT G.objid as HostGal_OBJID, GN.distance as NN1 FROM Galaxy as G SELECT r.BOSS_HEADS_RA as RA FROM MyDB.BOSS_HEADS_RA as r SELECT d.BOSS_HEADS_DEC as DEC FROM MyDB.BOSS_HEADS_DEC as d JOIN dbo.fGetNearbyObjEq (r.BOSS_HEADS_RA, d.BOSS_HEADS_DEC, #) AS GN ON G.objID = GN.objID ORDER BY distance OFFSET # ROWS /*Skip first # rows*/ FETCH NEXT # ROWS ONLY
